\rWhere other regions have teams (such as Rocket or Plasma) causing a ruckus around the region, Torren is home to a number of cults.
\rThe core difference between the cults and other Teams, is that the goals of the former have to do with the worship and catching of a legendary Pokemon.
\rThis is a stark contrast to groups like Team Rocket, who are in the search of money, money, and more money!
